  20 Aug 2006; Tiziano Müller <gentoo@dev-zero.ch> aria2-0.7.1.ebuild,
  +files/aria2-0.7.1-metalink_main_cc.patch:
  Patch for --disable-metalink compilation problem added (thanks to Zamorate
  for the discovery) Duplicated configure-line removed

  20 Aug 2006; Tiziano Müller <gentoo@dev-zero.ch> aria2-0.7.1.ebuild:
  Building with libxml2 support only if metalink is wanted

  17 Aug 2006; Tiziano Müller <gentoo@dev-zero.ch> -aria2-0.5.2.ebuild,
  -aria2-0.6.0_p1.ebuild, -aria2-0.6.0_p1-r1.ebuild,
