  +files/aria2-0.7.1-nameresolver_cc.patch,
  +files/aria2-0.7.1-nameresolver_h.patch:
  Fix for using c-ares as replacement for ares

  15 Aug 2006; Tiziano Müller <gentoo@dev-zero.ch> +aria2-0.7.1.ebuild:
  Version bump to v0.7.1 Upstream changed configure options (--enable-foo ->
  --with-foo) for many packages Upstream added support for c-ares library, USE
  flag added Cosmetic fixes

  08 Aug 2006; Josu López Fernández <zamorate@zamorate.net> ChangeLog:
  Adding again ~amd64 and ~ppc keywords

  08 Aug 2006; Tiziano Müller <gentoo@dev-zero.ch> +aria2-0.7.0.ebuild:
  Version bump to v0.7.0
  dodoc'ing ChangeLog now as well
  Some cosmetic cleanups

  03 Aug 2006; Tiziano Müller <gentoo@dev-zero.ch>
  +aria2-0.6.0_p1-r1.ebuild, +files/aria2-0.6.0_p1-http_header.patch:
